{"tid":143523,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人可以教吓我呢條stat題目點做","createTime":"2017-03-04T16:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T13:50:30.000Z","uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa40bf35b7aa96ffe044f31b3ff4ff669ceac57","tid":143523,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4mh54g8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4mh54g8.jpg&h=d64abe18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我淨係列佐f(x) 同E(X)出黎，之後就諗唔到點計好，求巴打們打救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2df3fd50423571712607931c7e0d5c42505132","tid":143523,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:33:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4mh54g8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4mh54g8.jpg&h=d64abe18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我淨係列佐f(x) 同E(X)出黎，之後就諗唔到點計好，求巴打們打救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁似newsvendor problem既"},{"pid":"ce482161068731ead5826f478e9d235fc08369d9","tid":143523,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:33:56.000Z","msg":"f(x) = 8 / Gamma(3) * x^2 * e ^ (-2x)<br />\nE(X) = 3 * 0.5 = 1.5"},{"pid":"81465f6e6d196d1c0b331de82d283579cc669403","tid":143523,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://na.cx/i/4mh54g8.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4mh54g8.jpg&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=56c27c75\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/4mh54g8.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n我淨係列佐f(x) 同E(X)出黎，之後就諗唔到點計好，求巴打們打救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁似newsvendor problem既</blockquote><br />\n普通stat 嘢黎<br />\n咁應該點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85edbf000c2417bac2a73483a004100bc4c38e39","tid":143523,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:46:31.000Z","msg":"我諗你要考慮 if production amount = k<br />\nfor demand X:<br />\nwhen 0&lt;x&lt;k, profit = 5*X + 1*(k - X) - 2*k<br />\nwhen x &gt; k, profit = 5*k - 2*k"},{"pid":"ff2a81fc3d11d35faad83b440bc39195ffca53bb","tid":143523,"uid":25065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:55:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce49840c147a1d0580fa1c27ae23857d080d5c60","tid":143523,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T17:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知咩distribution黎<br />\n<br />\n之前OM學，要搵<br />\nCu= (P-cost)<br />\nCo=(cost-salvage)<br />\n<br />\nProfit max when <br />\nP(D&lt;Q)=Cu/(Cu+Co)<br />\n<br />\n但我唔識你個個distribution"},{"pid":"7f9f9af4a38f1fd212e760a5d968453b13a91552","tid":143523,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T17:02:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知咩distribution黎<br />\n<br />\n之前OM學，要搵<br />\nCu= (P-cost)<br />\nCo=(cost-salvage)<br />\n<br />\nProfit max when <br />\nP(D&lt;Q)=Cu/(Cu+Co)<br />\n<br />\n但我唔識你個個distribution</blockquote><br />\nD for demand(random variable), Q for quantity prepared(decisiom)"},{"pid":"0bd40699a41fbc9153c32a3642382db2d083eedc","tid":143523,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T17:07:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://stats.stackexchange.com/questions/127094/maximize-the-profit-of-a-product-given-a-gamma-distribution\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstats.stackexchange.com%2Fquestions%2F127094%2Fmaximize-the-profit-of-a-product-given-a-gamma-distribution&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d684fdb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://stats.stackexchange.com/questions/127094/maximize-the-profit-of-a-product-given-a-gamma-distribution</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9cedec87a3e271df5e230ee1bd4ca2bb1ce143","tid":143523,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T17:20:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗你要考慮 if production amount = k<br />\nfor demand X:<br />\nwhen 0&lt;x&lt;k, profit = 5*X + 1*(k - X) - 2*k<br />\nwhen x &gt; k, profit = 5*k - 2*k</blockquote><br />\n如果分做兩個case，咁要點樣搵個expected value of profit<br />\n如果倒轉返拆條題目嘅話<br />\nE(Profit) 應該係等於 sum(ai*pi)<br />\na 係個profit, p 係probability, i = 1, 2, 3,...<br />\n但我又諗唔到點先做到呢一步"},{"pid":"f21229ddc4822bbc4436dc6d776cb6cd7c227fd4","tid":143523,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T17:20:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫完expected value條formula之後<br />\n用fundamental theorem of calculus?🤔</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以解多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4952b0fa69b4f3472ddbb8b486161df413bdfdd7","tid":143523,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T17:23:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知咩distribution黎<br />\n<br />\n之前OM學，要搵<br />\nCu= (P-cost)<br />\nCo=(cost-salvage)<br />\n<br />\nProfit max when <br />\nP(D&lt;Q)=Cu/(Cu+Co)<br />\n<br />\n但我唔識你個個distribution</blockquote><br />\nD for demand(random variable), Q for quantity prepared(decisiom)</blockquote><br />\n我諗個maximum expected value of profit 應該係用返derivative 去搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178d9fda07814083e13fea3384112322aeda4e3c","tid":143523,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T17:25:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://stats.stackexchange.com/questions/127094/maximize-the-profit-of-a-product-given-a-gamma-distribution\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstats.stackexchange.com%2Fquestions%2F127094%2Fmaximize-the-profit-of-a-product-given-a-gamma-distribution&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d684fdb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://stats.stackexchange.com/questions/127094/maximize-the-profit-of-a-product-given-a-gamma-distribution</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都google過條題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我完全唔明佢做緊乜嘢<br />\n同埋佢個答案同書嗰個唔一樣"},{"pid":"e4c2a306867b7aea84eb293c6bda61648d257397","tid":143523,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T17:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知咩distribution黎<br />\n<br />\n之前OM學，要搵<br />\nCu= (P-cost)<br />\nCo=(cost-salvage)<br />\n<br />\nProfit max when <br />\nP(D&lt;Q)=Cu/(Cu+Co)<br />\n<br />\n但我唔識你個個distribution</blockquote><br />\nD for demand(random variable), Q for quantity prepared(decisiom)</blockquote><br />\n我諗個maximum expected value of profit 應該係用返derivative 去搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地唔用calculus<br />\n<br />\n但應該係以下咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08MKOg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08MKOg6.jpg&h=eca60c21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e03d6d0468d4e024b616fa0797152ab6997631fd","tid":143523,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T17:41:32.000Z","msg":"我覺得似係寫左profit=咩先<br />\n再計E(profit)<br />\n再d佢 set to zero to maximize profit"},{"pid":"2ca414dc40aec66f76186bdf5632cc1c192b5ddd","tid":143523,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T17:48:05.000Z","msg":"未諗到點計 不過樓主個E(X)錯左<br />\n係3/0.5<br />\n因為係theta 唔係lambda"},{"pid":"9a3adf1dc97259a5a4b9a4c9039387f7259d28d2","tid":143523,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未諗到點計 不過樓主個E(X)錯左<br />\n係3/0.5<br />\n因為係theta 唔係lambda</blockquote><br />\n我個諗法同你上面嗰個一樣，但我唔識應該點set profit 條式<br />\n<br />\n另外我記得theta = mean waiting time for an occurrence<br />\nlambda = 1/theta = mean number of occurrences per unit time?<br />\n題目話 theta = units of days per 1000 units of rolls<br />\n同埋我見本書前面都係寫 mean = a * theta"},{"pid":"6fa6034af18e26db56da0f61c11c21b292555901","tid":143523,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:05:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>未諗到點計 不過樓主個E(X)錯左<br />\n係3/0.5<br />\n因為係theta 唔係lambda</blockquote><br />\n我個諗法同你上面嗰個一樣，但我唔識應該點set profit 條式<br />\n<br />\n另外我記得theta = mean waiting time for an occurrence<br />\nlambda = 1/theta = mean number of occurrences per unit time?<br />\n題目話 theta = units of days per 1000 units of rolls<br />\n同埋我見本書前面都係寫 mean = a * theta</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6gslhcxf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6gslhcxf&h=a8beaae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你試下in 好似好煩<br />\n<br />\nbtw你諗下theta個單位係per unit<br />\nx個單位係unit<br />\nE(X)個單位係unit<br />\n所以E(X)一定係要除theta先可以令到theta個單位係unit"},{"pid":"9d3483808463c230e70e7c1dec9c7f5de10e3624","tid":143523,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:08:44.000Z","msg":"如果你成功in到嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得下一步係d with respect to y, 唔係x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdda13806aada3bac414a2167d999797df6b5df9","tid":143523,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你成功in到嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得下一步係d with respect to y, 唔係x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你又啱，我無留意到呢度個x嘅單位同佢前面講嘅唔同<br />\n<br />\nok 我試吓先，thanks"},{"pid":"eba9ffd2f86dd73cb7f39f609cfef6d5a1f223ed","tid":143523,"uid":17021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:40:05.000Z","msg":"應該晤洗咁複雜....你用gamma 搵到P(X&gt;1)同P(X&lt;=1)<br />\n個expectation = Profit on Day 1*P(X&gt;1) + Profit On Day 2*P(X&lt;=1)<br />\n<br />\n利申: passed Exam P"},{"pid":"50274814df02b3ffa8dde04e5700dba59cc7b95f","tid":143523,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:48:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該晤洗咁複雜....你用gamma 搵到P(X&gt;1)同P(X&lt;=1)<br />\n個expectation = Profit on Day 1*P(X&gt;1) + Profit On Day 2*P(X&lt;=1)<br />\n<br />\n利申: passed Exam P</blockquote><br />\n我都passed exam p<br />\n不過巴打 X係unit of 包喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10c62f878a5ba3ba36896053437ea3f00695b66","tid":143523,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:49:23.000Z","msg":"好，唔該曬上面嘅巴打們，我聽日起身再試試做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04d7ebff62bdcfa910e9122e8bfce883822d39b","tid":143523,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T20:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>未諗到點計 不過樓主個E(X)錯左<br />\n係3/0.5<br />\n因為係theta 唔係lambda</blockquote><br />\n我個諗法同你上面嗰個一樣，但我唔識應該點set profit 條式<br />\n<br />\n另外我記得theta = mean waiting time for an occurrence<br />\nlambda = 1/theta = mean number of occurrences per unit time?<br />\n題目話 theta = units of days per 1000 units of rolls<br />\n同埋我見本書前面都係寫 mean = a * theta</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6gslhcxf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6gslhcxf&h=a8beaae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你試下in 好似好煩<br />\n<br />\nbtw你諗下theta個單位係per unit<br />\nx個單位係unit<br />\nE(X)個單位係unit<br />\n所以E(X)一定係要除theta先可以令到theta個單位係unit</blockquote><br />\nX&gt;Y既情況，其實佢有d profit因為唔夠貨而賺唔到，係咪要當佢cost咁減翻？(opportunity cost)"},{"pid":"2e76c07e9bd96da1265abb5e61566835d7d8c432","tid":143523,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T20:35:26.000Z","msg":"巴打，你搵下邊個Q會令P(D&lt;Q)=3/4？<br />\n<br />\n個答案岩唔岩？"}]}